## Usage Tiers

While the code is MIT-licensed, the hosted validation service
(api.pigmil.com) that powers domain-based feature gating is a separate
commercial service with the following tiers:

### Free tier (default)

- Up to **1,000 requests / day** per domain
- Up to **30,000 requests / month** per domain
- PIGMIL attribution shown in the widget footer

### Full / White-label tier

- Unlimited requests
- No PIGMIL branding
- Custom domain support

For full-tier access contact **webmaster@pigmil.com** or visit **pigmil.com**.
